伊拉克建造1000所学校。 据报道，近年来，中伊关系取得了长足发展。自1981年中国石油工程建设公司在伊拉克开始运营以来，中伊能源合作一直是两国关系的基石。如今，中国公司已涉足伊拉克石油行业的上游、中游和下游业务。另一方面，伊拉克也是中国最大的原油供应国之一。 \t2003年，中国曾强烈反对伊拉克战争，并呼吁有关国家停止军事行动。在伊拉克战争爆发近20年后，从绿色能源和重油工厂到道路和学校的建设，中国正将数十亿元人民币的资金投资于伊拉克各种各样的项目。报道称，目前，伊拉克目前已成为中国“一带一路”倡议的关键一环。 \t复旦大学绿色金融研究中心报告称，2021年伊拉克在“一带一路”基础设施倡议下获得了105亿美元（约合703亿元人民币）的投资。 \t伊拉克已成为中国在“一带一路”倡议下能源相关领域的第三大合作伙伴，仅次于俄罗斯和巴基斯坦。"},"attached_info":"Cj8I3uSAq6TdvdtlEAMaCDgyMDU1MTcwIJi/y5UGMBU4oQFAJnIJNTM4OTc5MjQ4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"25 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-ece42bfac12727eeec89101c684572fe_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"39_1656122195.2364292","card_id":"Q_20557776","target":{"id":20557776,"title":"部队里是怎样训练体能的？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/20557776","type":"question","created":1351308842,"answer_count":46,"follower_count":816,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[658,3229,33367],"comment_count":2,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"CjwI3uSAq6TdvdtlEAMaBjQwMzUzMCCqrK2EBTACOLAGQCdyCDIwNTU3Nzc2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"25 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-bb180851c13a81cedfb6f3d59e490b9d_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"40_1656122195.2368486","card_id":"Q_539550762","target":{"id":539550762,"title":"成都大运会新的举办日期确定为 2023 年 7 月 28 日至 8 月 8 日，将带来哪些影响？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/539550762","type":"question","created":1656118109,"answer_count":13,"follower_count":35,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1746,1897,25516,32781,2085956],"comment_count":1,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"据国际大体联官方消